<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 If I will be afraid of the darkest night
 You will turn on the stars for me in the blue sky
 And if I'll be worried by the deep sea
 You will take me over every big wave

[V2]
 Because great is Your love for me
 Because nothing is greater than You

[V3]
 You are the King
 You are the greatest
 Let everything that
 Has breathe praise You
 Your name is awesome
 Your hand is mighty
 Nothing is greater than You

[V4]
 I will reach every man who You'll make me meet
 And I will talk them about Your great love
 And they will sing the highest praise to Your name
 And they all together will lift up their hands

[V5]
 Because You are the great only King
 Because nothing is greater than You

[V6]
 You are the King...</lyrics>
<title>Nothing is greater than you</title>
<author>Nazireo</author>
<hymn_number>1741</hymn_number>
</song>